graph TD
    A[GET /toggle-detection Request] --> B[Check current detection state]
    B --> C{Is AI detection currently enabled?}
    C -- Yes, detection is enabled --> D[Log: Disabling AI package detection]
    C -- No, detection is disabled --> E[Log: Enabling AI package detection]
    D --> F[Set detection flag to disabled]
    E --> G[Set detection flag to enabled]
    F --> H[Return success response with disabled status]
    G --> I[Return success response with enabled status]
    H --> J[Request Complete]
    I --> J
